<div class="entry-header">
<h2 itemprop="name">
<a href="/blog/28-web-tips-and-tricks/bootstrap-tips-and-tricks/56-5-awesome-free-bootstrap-button-generators-online" itemprop="url">
5 awesome free Bootstrap button generators online</a>
</h2>
<dl class="article-info">
<dt class="article-info-term"></dt>
<dd class="createdby" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
<span itemprop="name" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Written by ">Arafat Bin Sultan</span> </dd>
<dd class="category-name">
<i class="fa fa-folder-open-o"></i>
<a href="/blog/28-web-tips-and-tricks/bootstrap-tips-and-tricks" itemprop="genre" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Article Category">Bootstrap Tips and Tricks</a> </dd>
<dd class="comment">
<i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i>
<span class="comments-anchor">
<a href="https://shapebootstrap.net/blog/28-web-tips-and-tricks/bootstrap-tips-and-tricks/56-5-awesome-free-bootstrap-button-generators-online#disqus_thread"></a>
</span>
</dd>
<dd class="create">
<i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
<time datetime="2016-03-02T14:51:38+06:00" itemprop="dateCreated" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Created Date">
