<dd class="create">
<i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
<time datetime="2016-02-24T13:08:18+06:00" itemprop="dateCreated" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Created Date">
24 February 2016 </time>
</dd>
<dd class="hits">
<span class="fa fa-eye"></span>
<meta itemprop="interactionCount" content="UserPageVisits:1400"/>
Hits: 1400</dd>
</dl>
</div>
<p>Bootstrap infrastructure includes several table styles that can fulfill most of your data visualisation needs. You get the basic, simple, row based table design to bordered and colored ones. These built-in table structures can lessen development time a lot. If you need more table functions, you may use additional plugins for this. I’ve gathered 5 free Bootstrap table plugins. Let’s see them.</p>
</article>
 
